<h4><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2020/08/13/apple-motion-sickness-vr-patent/">苹果更新基于 AR 的晕车解决方案专利</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358607" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot-2020-08-13-at-15.25.00.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="625" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot-2020-08-13-at-15.25.00.jpg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot-2020-08-13-at-15.25.00-360x281.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot-2020-08-13-at-15.25.00-768x600.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>MacRumours 消息，近日流出的专利显示苹果仍在更新一个基于 AR 的避免晕车解决方案。</p>
<p>专利文件显示，这个方案包含一个多用途的 VR 系统，用户可在汽车中通过沉浸式的 AR 体验替代实际可见的景色，这除了可用于娱乐外，还能作为一种避免晕车的方法 —— 将用户所见内容调整至不会为晕车者带来不适。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-08-13/apple-readies-apple-one-subscription-bundles-to-boost-services">苹果在筹备「Apple One」订阅服务套餐</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358609" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1x-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1330" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1x-1.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1x-1-360x239.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1x-1-768x511.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1x-1-1024x681.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>《彭博社》援引知情人士消息指出，苹果正筹备将多个数字服务打包成「Apple One」套餐，以更低价格推出，增加服务收入。据悉，Apple One 可能将于秋季发布会推出，并将分为多个收费等级：</p>
<p>基本款包括 Apple Music 和 Apple TV+ 服务；高级版则比基础版多出 Apple Arcade 游戏服务；再高一级版本则将多一个 Apple News+ 服务；最贵版本则将配有额外 iCloud 储存空间。</p>
