<h4><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2020/08/13/15-million-us-iphones-shipped-q2-2020/">iPhone 今年第二季度美国出货量达 1500 万部，创下新高</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358611" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iphone-se2-unpacking-8.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iphone-se2-unpacking-8.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iphone-se2-unpacking-8-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iphone-se2-unpacking-8-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>MacRumors 援引 Canalys 报告指出，今年的季度 iPhone 在美国的出货量达到 1500 万部，创下新纪录，同比增长达到 10%。报告指，第二季度出货的 iPhone 11 比去年增长了 15%，此外，iPhone SE 对增长也至关重要。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358612" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot-2020-08-13-at-09.38.46.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="417" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot-2020-08-13-at-09.38.46.jpg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot-2020-08-13-at-09.38.46-360x188.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot-2020-08-13-at-09.38.46-768x400.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>总的来说，美国智能手机出货量同比下降了 5%，但比 2020 年第一季度增长了 11%，报告将此归功于中国制造业和零售店的恢复。</p>
<h4>小狗电器 CEO 回应戴森诉讼，呼吁国内企业警惕专利壁垒</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358613" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pub.jpg" alt="" width="864" height="647" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pub.jpg 864w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pub-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pub-768x575.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 864px) 100vw, 864px" /></p>
<p>戴森与小狗电器的刷头外观专利诉讼进入一审判决阶段，法院初步支持戴森诉讼请求，该诉讼由戴森于 2017 年提起，时值小狗电器 IPO 关键时期。</p>
<p>爱范儿就此消息联络小狗电器 CEO 檀冲，他表示，小狗电器与戴森在全球各个市场都是直接竞争对手，而后者构建的专利壁垒在多个领域给小狗电器和一众国内品牌带来了挑战。此外，檀冲呼吁国内品牌注重核心技术的自主研发，成立行业联盟以共享专利资源，同时关注专利群生产业以获得竞争主动权。</p>
